{"tid":1305644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港加油, 認同就推] 不中擾敵之計 毋忘當初訴求","createTime":"2019-07-11T02:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:12:16.000Z","uid":1806,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9f39e58c83a1769ee34c852975ea8a4865cabc","tid":1305644,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:05:31.000Z","msg":"琴日單野大家有留意都會好嬲好氣憤, 請記住一切一切發生既問題都係源於政府出賣港人, 推出賣港政策, 加上制度上既不公, 議會暴力等等令香港變得唔再係昔日既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請不要忘記有義士為我地香港人犧牲<br />\n請不要忘記前線為我地香港人付出過既血汗同淚水<br />\n請不要忘記文宣為我地香港人日以繼夜付出既精神<br />\n<br />\n我地要專注返<strong>五大訴求</strong>同埋<strong>社會信用評分制度</strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 撤回草案 ❌<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義 ❌<br />\n3. 撤銷抗爭者控罪 ❌<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會 ❌<br />\n5. 落實雙普選 ❌<br />\n6. 撤回推行社會信用評分制度 🆕<br />\n7. 拆除所有智慧燈柱🆕</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n再大家要記住當日大家曾經講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做 <br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不割席 不督灰 不撤不散</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請相信身邊既巴絲<br />\n每一樣野從心出發深思熟慮後係有佢既意義, 會發揮到作用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>順度幫其他巴絲重要資訊forward 下D Links:<br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=1f0ae9ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=df3252ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 光復港大 守衛我城 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=1a2f7abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n7.13 - 光復上水 - <a href=\